Frances Chaney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frances_Chaney 0 Frances Chaney (July 23, 1915 - November 23, 2004) was an actress on stage, on old-time radio and on television. She was perhaps best known, however, for being "ostracized as pro-communist along with her late blacklisted husband, Ring Lardner Jr." Frances_Chaney ( July_23_,_1915 - November_23_,_2004 ) was an_actress on stage , on old-time_radio and on television .
